dc_title_s: Theatre de la guerre sur la coste de Coromandel.
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:1,346,852. Covers eastern coast of India from present-day Kothapatnam north to Porur. Shows residences and places of worship. Relief shown by landforms. Likely extracted from Abbe Prevost's Histoire Generale des Voyages."Suppl. au Tome IX Number 14"--Lower left margin. Includes key. In French. Dimensions: 30 x 23 centimeters
